
Reintermediation is an important aspect of P2P Media and the [[Attention Economy]]



=Definition=

From the Wikipedia article at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reintermediation


"Reintermediation can be defined as the reintroduction of an intermediary between end users (consumers) and a producer. This term applies especially to instances in which [[Disintermediation]] has occurred first."
(http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reintermediation)



